"AutoVerilog_GetInstModuleName 获取例化名和模块名{{{2
"--------------------------------------------------
" Function: AutoVerilog_GetInstModuleName
" Input: 
"   Must put cursor to /*autoinst*/ position
" Description:
" e.g
"   module_name #(
"       .A_PARAMETER (A_PARAMETER)
